comments: Tucker (PHI) and Jokic (DEN) engage and disengage with one another off-ball.
Tucker (PHI) establishes a legal guarding position in Jokic's (DEN) path and absorbs the incidental contact as they come together during the drive.
Tucker (PHI) brings his left arm forward slightly and marginal contact occurs with Jokic's (DEN) off-arm after Jokic takes his left hand away from the ball during his upward shooting motion.
Gordon (DEN) jumps vertically and incidental body contact occurs with Embiid (PHI) during the layup attempt.
Harden (PHI) legally contests Caldwell-Pope's (DEN) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Caldwell-Pope (DEN) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Harden (PHI) prior to incidental arm contact occurring.
Caldwell-Pope (DEN) again makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it from Harden (PHI) prior to incidental arm contact occurring.
Caldwell-Pope (DEN) avoids making contact with Harden (PHI) and legally contests the jump shot attempt.
Tucker (PHI) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Jokic (DEN), prior to the incidental arm contact that occurs.
Porter Jr. (DEN) brushes Harden's (PHI) right arm and marginal contact occurs as Harden passes the ball.
Harden (PHI) goes to, not through, Gordon's (DEN) front and marginal contact occurs. Gordon's reaction is not consistent with the amount of contact.
Gordon (DEN) moves forward slightly prior to marginal contact occurring with Harden's (PHI) left arm/side as Harden begins to pass.
Embiid (PHI) gathers the ball on his right foot and takes two steps before starting his upward shooting motion.

Embiid (PHI) jumps toward Jokic (DEN) to defend the inbound pass and he makes clean contact with the ball as simultaneous incidental arm contact occurs when Jokic passes the ball back toward the wing.
Tucker (PHI) and Jokic (DEN) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Embiid (PHI) brings his hands toward Gordon's (DEN) path and marginal contact occurs with Gordon's front as Gordon starts his drive.
Embiid (PHI) grabs and pulls Gordon's (DEN) jersey away from his body, which affects Gordon's SQBR during his driving shot attempt.
Murray (DEN) wraps his arm around Harris' (PHI) upper body and initiates contact that affects Harris' FOM along the sideline.
Caldwell-Pope (DEN) commits a take foul on Maxey (PHI).
Maxey (PHI) and Caldwell-Pope (DEN) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Caldwell-Pope (DEN) establishes himself in Harris' (PHI) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Harris (PHI) commits a take foul on Murray (DEN).
Maxey (PHI) and Caldwell-Pope (DEN) engage with one another after coming together at the same spot and quickly disengage as marginal contact occurs during the inbound.
Murray (DEN) brings his off-arm toward Harris' (PHI) side and releases away without applying any force as he stops his forward momentum.
Harris (PHI) legally contests Murray's (DEN) jump shot attempt.
